Description: SQL parser and transpiler (Avalan PPA pin)
 sqlglot is a Python SQL parser, transpiler, and optimizer that
 supports more than twenty dialects. This rebuild ships the pure-Python
 sqlglot library at 27.29.0 because Debian sid is on 30.x, above the
 upper bound Avalan tracks (>= 27.20, < 28). The optional Rust
 acceleration package (sqlglotrs) is not built here; sqlglot falls
 back to its pure-Python tokenizer when the extension is absent.
